casebody.data:
Teresa D'ANGELO, Petitioner-Movant,
v.
ARCHDIOCESE OF NEWARK/CHRIST THE KING PREPARATORY SCHOOL, Respondent-Respondent. M-897 September Term 2017
080368 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 23, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for counsel fees and costs is granted, in part. Counsel fees are awarded in the amount of $5,036.00 and costs are awarded in the amount of $93.40.
